		background: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
		text-align: center;
	}
	.jumbotron img {
		display: block;
		margin: auto;
	}
	/*
	 * Sometimes we need some additional space between rows.
	 */
	.top-buffer-3 { margin-top: 3%; }
	.top-buffer-2 { margin-top: 2%; }
	.top-buffer-1 { margin-top: 1%; }
